 <text>
  <front>
   <head>O THERE IS NOT A SHARPER DART.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="sestet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">O THERE is not a sharper dart</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Can pierce the mourner's suffering heart,</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Than when the friend we love and trust</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Tramples that friendship into dust, —</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Forgets the sacred, honour'd claim,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And proves it but an empty name!</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="sestet">
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">I almost as a sister lov'd thee,</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And thought that nothing could have mov'd thee!</l>
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">But, like the dewdrops on a spray</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">That shrinks before the morning ray, —</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Like the frail sunshine on the stream,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Thy friendship faded as a dream.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="sestet">
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">When sickness and when sorrow tried me,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Thy aid — thy friendship was denied me;</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Thy love was but a summer flower,</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And could not stand the wintry shower:</l>
     <l n="17" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">More for thyself than me I grieve</l>
     <l n="18" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Thou could'st thus cruelly deceive.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
